## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-329">Чтобы синхронно говорят строка, содержащая разметку SSML, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsml%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-329">To synchronously speak a string that contains SSML markup, use the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsml%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-330">Чтобы асинхронно произносить содержимое строки, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-330">To asynchronously speak the contents of a string, use the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-331">Как показано в следующем примере <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> метод предоставляет простейший средства для создания речи, вывод синхронно.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-331">As shown in the following example, the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> method provides the simplest means to generate speech output synchronously.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
      // Initialize a new instance of the SpeechSynthesizer.  
      using (SpeechSynthesizer synth = new SpeechSynthesizer())  
      {  
  
        // Configure the audio output.   
        synth.SetOutputToDefaultAudioDevice();  
  
        // Speak a string synchronously.  
        synth.Speak("What is your favorite color?");  
      }  
  
      Console.WriteLine();  
      Console.WriteLine("Press any key to exit...");  
      Console.ReadKey();  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-356">Вы можете отменить асинхронный воспроизводить запрос с <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancel%2A> или <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancelAll%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-356">You can cancel the asynchronous speaking of a prompt with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancel%2A> or the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancelAll%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-357">Чтобы синхронно произносить содержимое <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt> , используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-357">To synchronously speak the contents of a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt> object, use <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-358">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt> объект из строки и передает объект в качестве аргумента <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-358">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.Prompt> object from a string and passes the object as an argument to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
      // Initialize a new instance of the SpeechSynthesizer.  
      SpeechSynthesizer synth = new SpeechSynthesizer();  
  
      // Configure the audio output.   
      synth.SetOutputToDefaultAudioDevice();  
  
      // Create a prompt from a string.  
      Prompt color = new Prompt("What is your favorite color?");  
  
      // Speak the contents of the prompt asynchronously.  
      synth.SpeakAsync(color);  
  
      Console.WriteLine();  
      Console.WriteLine("Press any key to exit...");  
      Console.ReadKey();  
    }  
  }  
}  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-362">Чтобы синхронно произносить содержимое <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> , используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-362">To synchronously speak the contents of a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> object, use <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A>.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-363">В следующем примере создается <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> объект из строки и передает объект в качестве аргумента <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-363">The following example creates a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.PromptBuilder> object from a string and passes the object as an argument to the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
      // Initialize a new instance of the SpeechSynthesizer.  
      SpeechSynthesizer synth = new SpeechSynthesizer();  
  
      // Configure the audio output.   
      synth.SetOutputToDefaultAudioDevice();  
  
      // Create a PromptBuilder object and append a text string.  
      PromptBuilder song = new PromptBuilder();  
      song.AppendText("Say the name of the song you want to hear");  
  
      // Speak the contents of the prompt asynchronously.  
      synth.SpeakAsync(song);  
  
      Console.WriteLine();  
      Console.WriteLine("Press any key to exit...");  
      Console.ReadKey();  
    }  
  }  
}  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-367">Чтобы асинхронно говорят строка, содержащая разметку SSML, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsmlAsync%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-367">To asynchronously speak a string that contains SSML markup, use the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsmlAsync%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-368">Чтобы синхронно произносить содержимое строки, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-368">To synchronously speak the contents of a string, use the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-369">Вы можете отменить асинхронный воспроизводить запрос с <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancel%2A> или <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancelAll%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-369">You can cancel the asynchronous speaking of a prompt with the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancel%2A> or the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancelAll%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-370">Как показано в следующем примере <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> метод предоставляет простейший средства для создания речи, выходные данные асинхронно.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-370">As shown in the following example, the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> method provides the simplest means to generate speech output asynchronously.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
      // Initialize a new instance of the SpeechSynthesizer.  
      SpeechSynthesizer synth = new SpeechSynthesizer();  
  
      // Configure the audio output.   
      synth.SetOutputToDefaultAudioDevice();  
  
      // Speak a string asynchronously.  
      synth.SpeakAsync("What is your favorite color?");  
  
      Console.WriteLine();  
      Console.WriteLine("Press any key to exit...");  
      Console.ReadKey();  
    }  
  }  
}  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-380">В следующем примере показано использование <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancelAll%2A> для отмены асинхронного воспроизводить запрос, таким образом, может произнести новую строку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-380">The following example show a use of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsyncCancelAll%2A> to cancel the asynchronous speaking of a prompt, so that a new prompt can be spoken.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-381">Обратите внимание, что <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakCompleted> при нажатии <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> операция отменяется.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-381">Note that the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakCompleted> event fires when a <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakAsync%2A> operation is cancelled.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
using System.Threading;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
      // Initialize a new instance of the SpeechSynthesizer.  
      SpeechSynthesizer synth = new SpeechSynthesizer();  
  
      // Configure the audio output.   
      synth.SetOutputToDefaultAudioDevice();  
  
      // Subscribe to the StateChanged event.  
      synth.StateChanged += new EventHandler<StateChangedEventArgs>(synth_StateChanged);  
  
      // Subscribe to the SpeakProgress event.  
      synth.SpeakProgress += new EventHandler<SpeakProgressEventArgs>(synth_SpeakProgress);  
  
      // Subscribe to the SpeakCompleted event.  
      synth.SpeakCompleted += new EventHandler<SpeakCompletedEventArgs>(synth_SpeakCompleted);  
  
      // Begin speaking a text string asynchronously.  
      synth.SpeakAsync("Speech is an effective and natural way for people to interact with applications, " +  
        "complementing or even replacing the use of mice, keyboards, controllers, and gestures.");  
  
      // Speak for four seconds.  
      Thread.Sleep(4000);  
  
      // Cancel the SpeakAsync operation and wait one second.  
      synth.SpeakAsyncCancelAll();  
      Thread.Sleep(1000);  
  
      // Speak a new text string.  
      synth.Speak("An urgent email message has arrived. Do you want to hear it?");  
  
      Console.WriteLine();  
      Console.WriteLine("Press any key to exit...");  
      Console.ReadKey();  
    }  
  
    // Write to the console when the SpeakAsync operation has been cancelled.  
    static void synth_SpeakCompleted(object sender, SpeakCompletedEventArgs e)  
    {  
      Console.WriteLine("\nThe SpeakAsync operation was cancelled!!");  
    }  
  
    // When it changes, write the state of the SpeechSynthesizer to the console.  
    static void synth_StateChanged(object sender, StateChangedEventArgs e)  
    {  
      Console.WriteLine("\nSynthesizer State: {0}    Previous State: {1}\n", e.State, e.PreviousState);  
    }  
  
    // Write the text being spoken by the SpeechSynthesizer to the console.  
    static void synth_SpeakProgress(object sender, SpeakProgressEventArgs e)  
    {  
      Console.WriteLine(e.Text);  
    }      
  }    
}  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-391">Содержание `textToSpeak` параметр должен содержать `speak` элемент и должны соответствовать [языка разметки синтеза речи (SSML) версии 1.0](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=201763).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-391">The contents of the `textToSpeak` parameter must include a `speak` element and must conform to the [Speech Synthesis Markup Language (SSML) Version 1.0](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=201763).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-392">Дополнительные сведения см. в разделе [Справочник по языку разметки синтеза речи](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/0c51279e-84d2-4f73-a924-8832039abf94).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-392">For more information, see [Speech Synthesis Markup Language Reference](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/0c51279e-84d2-4f73-a924-8832039abf94).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-393">Чтобы асинхронно говорят строка, содержащая разметку SSML, используйте <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsmlAsync%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-393">To asynchronously speak a string that contains SSML markup, use the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsmlAsync%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-394">Можно использовать <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> инициировать синхронной говоря о строке, которая содержит разметку SSML.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-394">You can use <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.Speak%2A> to initiate the synchronous speaking of a string that does not contain SSML markup.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-395">Во время вызова этого метода <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer> может инициировать следующие события:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-395">During a call to this method, the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer> can raise the following events:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-396"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.StateChanged>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-396"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.StateChanged>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-397">Вызывается, когда изменяется состояние произношения синтезатора.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-397">Raised when the speaking state of the synthesizer changes.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-398"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakStarted>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-398"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakStarted>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-399">Вызывается, когда начинается синтезатор создания речи.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-399">Raised when the synthesizer begins generating speech.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-400"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.PhonemeReached>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-400"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.PhonemeReached>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-401">Возникает каждый раз, когда достигает синтезатор буквы или сочетание букв, которые составляют скрытые звука речи на языке.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-401">Raised each time the synthesizer reaches a letter or combination of letters that constitute a discreet sound of speech in a language.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-402"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakProgress>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-402"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakProgress>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-403">Возникает каждый раз синтезатор завершается, говоря слова.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-403">Raised each time the synthesizer completes speaking a word.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-404"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.VisemeReached>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-404"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.VisemeReached>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-405">Возникает каждый раз, текст требует изменения положения рот или лиц мышцы, использовавшихся для создания речи.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-405">Raised each time spoken output requires a change in the position of the mouth or the facial muscles used to produce speech.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-406"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.BookmarkReached>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-406"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.BookmarkReached>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-407">Вызывается, когда синтезатор сталкивается с закладкой, введите в командной строке.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-407">Raised when the synthesizer encounters a bookmark in a prompt.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="973e8-408"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.VoiceChange>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-408"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.VoiceChange>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="973e8-409">Возникает при изменении голоса для синтезатор.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-409">Raised when the speaking voice for the synthesizer changes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-410"><xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer> Не вызывает <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakCompleted> событие при обработке <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsml%2A> метод.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-410">The <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer> does not raise the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakCompleted> event while processing the <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.SpeechSynthesizer.SpeakSsml%2A> method.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="973e8-411">Следующий пример отображает дату 1/29/2009, как дата, месяц, день, год заказа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="973e8-411">The following example renders the date 1/29/2009 as a date, in month, day, year order.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System;  
using System.Speech.Synthesis;  
  
namespace SampleSynthesis  
{  
  class Program  
  {  
    static void Main(string[] args)  
    {  
  
      // Initialize a new instance of the SpeechSynthesizer.  
      SpeechSynthesizer synth = new SpeechSynthesizer();  
  
      // Configure the audio output.   
      synth.SetOutputToDefaultAudioDevice();  
  
      // Build an SSML prompt in a string.  
      string str = "<speak version=\"1.0\"";  
      str += " xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/10/synthesis\"";  
      str += " xml:lang=\"en-US\">";  
      str += "<say-as type=\"date:mdy\"> 1/29/2009 </say-as>";  
      str += "</speak>";  
  
      // Speak the contents of the prompt synchronously.
      synth.SpeakSsml(str);  
  
      Console.WriteLine("Press any key to exit...");  
      Console.ReadKey();  
    }  
  }  
}  
```

  
  
